::The Eletors/Firearm/Prowl::

The Eletors exit their ship, looking around to see if any enemies 
were still fighting. The only ones they saw battling were Prowl and 
Iron Raptor, but otherwise things were peaceful. They had left 
Firearm in a CR chamber programmed to keep him in stasis lock untill 
they returned, so that he wouldn't snap and try to get out of the 
ship.

"Lets combine and split those two up," Mantle says and all of the 
Eletors launch into the air, forming different parts of Element. Soon 
the gestalt emerges from behind the shields of his ship, heading over 
toward Prowl and Iron Raptor.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Prowl yells out in pain as Iron Raptor's teeth tear through his wing. 
He jerks it out of the way, resulting in a loud crack and another 
roar from him. His wing was broken. Prowl opens his jaws, about to 
bite Iron Raptor in the neck again. He lunges forward, but a huge 
hand suddenly wraps around his neck, jerking him off of Iron Raptor. 
Prowl tries to struggle and get away, but the hand was too powerful, 
lifting him high into the air.

Element reaches down with his other hand, trying to pick up IR.
